\c 2
\s Timotio anosimbiswa
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo iwe, mwana wangu, simba munyasha dziri muna Kristu Jesu.
\v 2 Nezvinhu zvawakanzwa kwandiri pakati pezvapupu zvizhinji, uzvikumikidze izvozvo kuvanhu vakatendeka vachagonawo kudzidzisa vamwe.
\v 3 Naizvozvo iwe utambudzike zvakaoma, semurwi wakanaka waJesu Kristu.
\v 4 Hakuna munhu anobata semurwi anozvipinganidza nezviitiko zveupenyu, kuti afadze uyo waka\add mu\add*pinza basa.
\v 5 Uye kana munhuwo achikwikwidza, haashongedzwi korona kana asina kukwikwidza zviri pamurairo.
\v 6 Murimi anobata zvakasimba anofanira kutanga kugamuchira zvibereko.
\v 7 Fungisisa zvandinoreva; uye Ishe ngaakupe kunzwisisa pazvinhu zvose.
\p
\v 8 Rangarira Jesu Kristu wakamutswa kubva kuvakafa, wembeu yaDhavhidhi, zvichienderana neevhangeri yangu;
\v 9 yandinotambudzika mairi zvakaipa, kusvika pazvisungo, semuiti wezvakaipa; asi shoko raMwari harina kusungwa.
\v 10 Saka ndinotsungirira zvinhu zvose nekuda kwevakasanangurwa, kuti naivo vawane ruponeso rwuri muna Kristu Jesu, pamwe nekubwinya kusingaperi.
\v 11 Shoko \add iri\add* rakatendeka; nokuti kana takafa pamwe \add naye\add*, tichararamawo pamwe \add naye\add*.
\v 12 Kana tikatsungirira, tichatongawo pamwe na\add ye\add*; kana tika\add mu\add*ramba, naiye achatiramba.
\v 13 Kana tisingatendeki, iye anoramba akatendeka; iye haagoni kuzviramba.
\s Tinofanira kuita sei kune vakarasika padzidzo
\p
\v 14 U\add va\add*rangaridze zvinhu izvi, uchirairisa pamberi paIshe kusapikisa pamashoko kusingabatsiri chinhu \add asi\add* kutsausa vanonzwa.
\v 15 Shingaira kuti uzviratidze kuna Mwari uri wakatendeka, mushandi asingafaniri kunyadziswa, anonyatsoruramisa shoko rechokwadi.
\v 16 Asi nzvenga kutaura kwetsvina kusina maturo; nokuti vacharamba vachingonyanya pakusatya Mwari,
\v 17 neshoko ravo richanyenga segomarara; pakati pavo pana Himenayosi naFiretosi;
\v 18 ivo vakatsauka pachokwadi, vachiti kumuka kwatova\add po\add*, vachipidigura rutendo rwevamwe.
\v 19 Kunyange zvakadaro nheyo yaMwari inomira yakasimba, ine mucherechedzo uyu: Ishe anoziva vari vake, uye \add kuti\add*: Umwe neumwe anoreva zita raKristu ngaabve pakusarurama.
\v 20 Asi mumba huru hamuna midziyo yegoridhe neyesirivha chete, asiwo yematanda neyevhu, uye imwe ndeyekukudzwa asi imwe ndeyekusakudzwa.
\v 21 Naizvozvo kana munhu achizvinatsa pazvinhu izvi, achava mudziyo wekukudzwa, wakaitwa mutsvene, une basa kuna Tenzi, wakagadzirirwa basa rose rakanaka.
\p
\v 22 Tizawo kuchiva kweudiki, asi uteverere kururama, rutendo, rudo, rugare, pamwe nevanodana kuna Ishe zvichibva pamoyo wakachena.
\v 23 Asi mibvunzo yeupenzi neyekusadzidza urambe, uchiziva kuti zvinomutsa kurwa.
\v 24 Zvino muranda waIshe haafaniri kurwa, asi ave munyoro kune vese, anoziva kudzidzisa, ane moyo murefu,
\v 25 anoraira neunyoro avo vanozvipikisa, kuti zvimwe Mwari avape kutendeukira kuruzivo rwechokwadi,
\v 26 uye vapengenuke kubva pamusungo wadhiabhorosi, wavaiva vakabatwa naye pakuda kwake.